text: Kumasi Technical Institute is a coeducational second-cycle technical school in Kumasi in the Ashanti Region of Ghana ==History== The school was established in 1976 with support from the government of Ghana. ==See also== * Education in Ghana * List of senior high schools in the Ashanti Region ==References== ==External links== * , the school's official website Category:1976 establishments in Ghana Category:Educational institutions established in 1976 Category:High schools in Ghana Category:Education in Kumasi Category:Public schools Category:Technical schools
